pe\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"1777  \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"1778  /* Display the macro variables */\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"1779  %put &num_vars;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"regionPctCustomers numOfTotalReturns wksSinceLastPurch basktPurchCount12Month LastPurchaseAmount AvgPurchaseAmountTotal \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"normal\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"intAdExposureCount36 intAdExposureCountAll socialMediaAdCount12 socialMediaAdCount36 totalNumProdPurchased custInitiatedContacts \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"normal\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"avgDiscountValue12 customersales wksSinceFirstPurch EstimatedIncome regionMedHomeVal techSupportEval customerAge AvgPurchasePerAd12\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"normal\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"1780  %put &char_vars;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"customerGender customerSubscrStat DemHomeOwner\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"normal\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"1781  %put &target;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"LostCustomer\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"normal\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"1782  ;*';*\\\";*/;run;quit;ods html5(id=vscode) close;\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"1783  \",\n\t\t\"type\": \"source\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\t\"line\": \"\",\n\t\t\"type\": \"note\",\n\t\t\"version\": 1\n\t}\n]","mime":"application/vnd.sas.compute.log.lines"}]}]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"## Data Partitioning\n\nPartitions data using Surveyselect procedure into stratified training and testing partitions using an 70/30 split.","outputs":[]},{"kind":2,"language":"sas","value":"proc sort data=work.customer_churn_ml;\